<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[متأ]</span>: مَتَأَه بالعصا،<span class="c5"> مهموز:</span> أي ضربه بها.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>... فَعُلَ، يَفْعُل، بالضم<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
